	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think this is a great idea.  I would also like to help with the project.
<br />
<br />Some features I would like to see in an ASM would be:
<br />1. Cycle counting
<br />2. A hex view of the machine code and editor.
<br />3. CPU emulator
<br />4. Controller simulation
<br />5. Subroutines and Macros
<br />6. Tile editing
<br />7. Music editing
<br />
<br />Private Message me if you want email information.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
